Microcontroler: 
Arduino Uno R3 (ATMEGA328P)

Sensors:
DHT11 - Temperature and humidity
Termistor NTC - Temperature (for water)

BLuetooth: 
HM-10 (BLE) - 10m

Power supply:
18650 3,7V 1A 2000mAh - (step-up module for 5V output)
Li-Po 3,7v 1A 2000mAh - (step-up module for 5V output)

Motor:
Dual H-Bridge HG7881 (L9110S) - Motor control
2x DC 1.5-3V RE-140RA ~5700RPM (1.5V) and ~11000RPM (3V)
